== Births == * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 18th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1641]] {{ill|October 5|ja|10月5日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Kira Yoshihisa|ja|吉良義央|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, lord of the Tokugawa high family (died [[1702]]). * [[Kansei]] 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1791]] {{ill|September 29|ja|9月29日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Sanada Yukinori|ja|真田幸貫|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 8th lord of the Matsushiro Domain (died [[1852]]). * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1828]] {{ill|October 10|ja|10月10日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Matsudaira Harugaku|ja|松平春嶽|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, lord of the late Edo-period Echizen Domain and a government minister (died [[1890]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 12nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1841]] {{ill|October 16|ja|10月16日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Itō Hirobumi|ja|伊藤博文|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a statesman who served as Prime Minister of Japan in the 1st, 5th, 7th, and 10th administrations (died [[1909]]). * [[Meiji era|Meiji]] 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1871]] {{ill|October 15|ja|10月15日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Kōya Iwasaburō|ja|高野岩三郎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a social statistician and social activist (died [[1949]]).
== Deaths == * [[Emperor Kaika]] 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[158 BC]] {{ill|October 14|ja|10月14日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Emperor Kōgen|ja|孝元天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 8th Emperor of Japan. * [[Karoku]] 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1227]] {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Horikawa Tōkugu|ja|堀川通具|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a waka poet (born [[1171]]). == Commemorations == {{Empty section|date=2021}}
