== Births == * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 18th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1641]] {{ill|October 5|ja|10月5日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Kira Yoshihisa|ja|吉良義央|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, lord of the Tokugawa high family (died [[1702]]). * [[Kansei]] 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1791]] {{ill|September 29|ja|9月29日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Sanada Yukinori|ja|真田幸貫|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 8th lord of the Matsushiro Domain (died [[1852]]). * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1828]] {{ill|October 10|ja|10月10日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Matsudaira Harugaku|ja|松平春嶽|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, lord of the late Edo-period Echizen Domain and a government minister (died [[1890]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 12nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1841]] {{ill|October 16|ja|10月16日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Itō Hirobumi|ja|伊藤博文|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a statesman who served as Prime Minister of Japan in the 1st, 5th, 7th, and 10th administrations (died [[1909]]). * [[Meiji era|Meiji]] 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1871]] {{ill|October 15|ja|10月15日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Kōya Iwasaburō|ja|高野岩三郎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a social statistician and social activist (died [[1949]]).
