== Events == * {{ill|Reiki|ja|霊亀|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft}} [[715]] {{ill|October 2|ja|10月2日|qq=draft}}) – Following the presentation of the "Suikime" (瑞亀献上), the era name was changed from {{ill|Wadō|ja|和銅|qq=draft|qq=draft}} to {{ill|Reiki|ja|霊亀|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Kennin|ja|建仁|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft}} [[1203]] {{ill|October 7|ja|10月7日|qq=draft}}) – In the incident known as the "Hikii Nōin no Hen" (比企能員の変), the anti-shogunate plot led by the relative of [[Minamoto no Yoriie]] (外戚・比企能員) against {{ill|Hojo Tokimasa|ja|北条時政|qq=draft}} was uncovered, and the conspirators were executed. * {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft}} [[1863]] {{ill|October 14|ja|10月14日|qq=draft}}) – The "Idogataya Incident" (井土ヶ谷事件) occurred. * [[Meiji era|Meiji]] 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft}} [[1871]] {{ill|October 14|ja|10月14日|qq=draft}}) – The government reformed official salaries, switching from an annual salary system to a monthly payment system.
== Births == * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 18th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft}} [[1641]] {{ill|October 5|ja|10月5日|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Kira Yoshihisa|ja|吉良義央|qq=draft}}, lord of the Tokugawa high family (died [[1702]]). * [[Kansei]] 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft}} [[1791]] {{ill|September 29|ja|9月29日|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Sanada Yukinori|ja|真田幸貫|qq=draft}}, the 8th lord of the Matsushiro Domain (died [[1852]]). * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft}} [[1828]] {{ill|October 10|ja|10月10日|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Matsudaira Harugaku|ja|松平春嶽|qq=draft}}, lord of the late Edo-period Echizen Domain and a government minister (died [[1890]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 12nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft}} [[1841]] {{ill|October 16|ja|10月16日|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Itō Hirobumi|ja|伊藤博文|qq=draft}}, a statesman who served as Prime Minister of Japan in the 1st, 5th, 7th, and 10th administrations (died [[1909]]). * [[Meiji era|Meiji]] 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft}} [[1871]] {{ill|October 15|ja|10月15日|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Kōya Iwasaburō|ja|高野岩三郎|qq=draft}}, a social statistician and social activist (died [[1949]]).
== Deaths == * [[Emperor Kaika]] 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft}} [[158 BC]] {{ill|October 14|ja|10月14日|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Emperor Kōgen|ja|孝元天皇|qq=draft}}, the 8th Emperor of Japan. * [[Karoku]] 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft}} [[1227]] {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Horikawa Tōkugu|ja|堀川通具|qq=draft}}, a waka poet (born [[1171]]). == Commemorations == {{Empty section|date=2021}}
