== Births == * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 18th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1641]] {{ill|October 5|ja|10月5日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Kira Yoshihisa|ja|吉良義央|qq=draft|qq=}}, lord of the Tokugawa high family (died [[1702]]). * [[Kansei]] 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1791]] {{ill|September 29|ja|9月29日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Sanada Yukinori|ja|真田幸貫|qq=draft|qq=}}, the 8th lord of the Matsushiro Domain (died [[1852]]). * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1828]] {{ill|October 10|ja|10月10日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Matsudaira Harugaku|ja|松平春嶽|qq=draft|qq=}}, lord of the late Edo-period Echizen Domain and a government minister (died [[1890]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 12nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1841]] {{ill|October 16|ja|10月16日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Itō Hirobumi|ja|伊藤博文|qq=draft|qq=}}, a statesman who served as Prime Minister of Japan in the 1st, 5th, 7th, and 10th administrations (died [[1909]]). * [[Meiji era|Meiji]] 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1871]] {{ill|October 15|ja|10月15日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Kōya Iwasaburō|ja|高野岩三郎|qq=draft|qq=}}, a social statistician and social activist (died [[1949]]).
== Deaths == * [[Emperor Kaika]] 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=}} [[158 BC]] {{ill|October 14|ja|10月14日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Emperor Kōgen|ja|孝元天皇|qq=draft|qq=}}, the 8th Emperor of Japan. * [[Karoku]] 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=}} [[1227]] {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|qq=draft|qq=}}) – {{ill|Horikawa Tōkugu|ja|堀川通具|qq=draft|qq=}}, a waka poet (born [[1171]]). == Commemorations == {{Empty section|date=2021|qq=}}
